                                            <td valign="top" class="bodyContent" mc:edit="body_content00">
                                                <h2>Order number: {{orderNumber}}</h2>
                                                <p>Dear {{customer.name}}</p>
                                                <p>Thank you for your order. We heard you loud and clear, and will try to delivery everthing to you as soon as possible within the next 45 minutes. In the mean time if you have any queries in regards to your order, please do not hesitate to call us on 023 8206 0491 or email us on cloud7shisha@outlook.com.</p>
