                                                <p>Order received: {{dt date}} at {{tm date}}</p>
                                                <p>Order requested: {{deliveryTime}}</p>
                                                <p>Comment: {{comment}}</p>
                                                <p>We will deliver your order to: {{deliveryAddress.streetNumber}} {{deliveryAddress.streetName}}, {{deliveryAddress.city}}, {{deliveryAddress.postcode}}</p>                                            
                                            </td>
